agation can be achieved in\nregimes of sufficiently regularized variational dynamics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 May 2021 17:55:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 May 2021 17:07:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 21 Nov 2021 19:49:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-18"}
