-mass planetary embryos formed around\n$\\gtrapprox$1.0~au. Finally, our simulations produce a steep radial mass\ndistribution of planetesimals in the terrestrial region which is qualitatively\naligned with formation models suggesting that the asteroid belt was born\nlow-mass.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 May 2021 18:12:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-14"}
