tion temperatures which could\nresult in the hysteresis. This work shows the potential of using nanomechanical\nresonance to characterize the CDW in suspended 2D materials and demonstrate\nthat degradation can have a large effect on transition temperatures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 May 2021 23:23:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-05"}
