lity\nplacement is NP-hard and that this result holds for all feasible client weight\ndistributions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 May 2021 11:27:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 Aug 2021 13:34:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-19"}
