etworks, by leveraging the open radio\naccess network (O-RAN) architecture with appropriate real-time engines and\nnetwork interfaces for collecting necessary machine learning data. Therefore,\nthis work provides novel research directions to design machine learning based\ncomponents that contribute towards i-ZTA for the future 5G/6G networks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 May 2021 13:14:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Feb 2022 14:50:50 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 27 Jul 2022 13:33:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-28"}
